title: Video: YOUTHCULT – Bored
body:
Swedish outfit **YOUTHCULT** cropped up in [October](http://admin.

crackintheroad.com/music/24537-introducing-y-o-u-t-h-c-u-l-t/) of last year and have kept things fairly under wraps since then. Still no identities attached to the project, and new video for recent track _Bored_ doesn’t reveal anything more substantial either. As with their debut YOUTHC\*NT EP, Bored straddles the middle ground between the epic, stadium suited rock of WU LYF and the beauteous, more elegant compositions associated with Manchester outfit MONEY. It’s a huge sound.
